question.value:
Participants can be of three types: 
(1) Amazon Mechanical Turk (MTurk) workers who are currently adult, aged 18 years and above, living in the United States; 
(2) participants recruited from online forums, such as Facebook, Reddit, and other online communities who are currently adult, aged 18 years and above, living in the United States; 
(3) Duke Psychology &amp; Neuroscience subject pool available through Sona systems. Sona participants must be aged 18 years and above, and to be living in the United States at the time of the survey.

